<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 06:20:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>TikTok母公司字节跳动创始人跃居中国富豪榜榜首</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/founder-tiktok-owner-bytedance-jumps-top-chinas-rich-list-2024-10-29/</link><description>周二公布的年度富豪榜显示，字节跳动创始人张一鸣是中国首富，个人财富为 493 亿美元，尽管房地产和可再生能源领域的同行表现不佳。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:36:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/founder-tiktok-owner-bytedance-jumps-top-chinas-rich-list-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>卢比与人民币疲软和当地股市下跌作斗争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-battles-yuan-weakness-losses-local-equities-2024-10-29/</link><description>由于人民币贬值以及外资流出导致当地股市下跌，印度卢比周二仍面临压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:30:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-battles-yuan-weakness-losses-local-equities-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>什么是“台独”？台湾已经独立了吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-is-taiwan-independence-is-taiwan-already-independent-2024-10-29/</link><description>中国表示不会放弃使用武力将台湾置于其控制之下。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-is-taiwan-independence-is-taiwan-already-independent-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国习近平敦促拜登改变对台湾问题的措辞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-pressed-biden-alter-language-taiwan-sources-say-2024-10-29/</link><description>消息人士告诉路透社，中国希望美国说“我们反对台独”，而不是目前的版本，即美国“不支持”台独。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-pressed-biden-alter-language-taiwan-sources-say-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰第三季度利润超预期，启动30亿美元回购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-third-quarter-profit-rises-10-beats-estimates-2024-10-29/</link><description>汇丰控股周二公布第三季度利润增长 10%，超出分析师预期，原因是其财富和批发银行业务受益于低于预期的降息，同时该公司开始了其历史上最大规模的改革之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 04:14:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-third-quarter-profit-rises-10-beats-estimates-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将利用神舟十九号将第十四次载人航天任务送入太空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-send-14th-crewed-mission-space-shenzhou-19-2024-10-29/</link><description>中国将于周三将三名宇航员送入近地轨道，这是该国第14次载人航天任务，届时将进行数十项科学实验。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 03:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-send-14th-crewed-mission-space-shenzhou-19-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>面对美国国债收益率上升和资金外流，卢比将保持挑衅态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-remain-defiant-face-higher-us-yields-outflows-2024-10-29/</link><description>印度卢比周二开盘可能几乎没有变化，在印度储备银行可能进行干预的情况下，对美国国债收益率、资本外流和其他外部信号反应迟钝。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 02:51:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-remain-defiant-face-higher-us-yields-outflows-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官抵达台湾，官员淡化特朗普言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/senior-us-diplomat-arrives-taiwan-officials-downplay-trump-comments-2024-10-29/</link><description>美国事实上的大使馆周二表示，一名帮助管理与台湾关系的美国高级外交官已抵达台北，台湾官员试图淡化唐纳德·特朗普最近对台湾关键芯片产业和国防需求的攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 02:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/senior-us-diplomat-arrives-taiwan-officials-downplay-trump-comments-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告深海间谍装置和引导外国潜艇的水下“灯塔”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-warns-deep-sea-spying-devices-underwater-lighthouses-that-guide-foreign-2024-10-29/</link><description>中国国家安全部周二表示，已在海面和深处发现了间谍装置，其中包括可以引导外国潜艇通行的水下“灯塔”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 01:56:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-warns-deep-sea-spying-devices-underwater-lighthouses-that-guide-foreign-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>Polestar表示拜登的提议将“有效禁止”其汽车在美国销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/biden-proposal-would-effectively-prohibit-sale-polestar-cars-us-automaker-says-2024-10-28/</link><description>Polestar周一表示，拜登政府拟议的禁止使用中国汽车硬件和软件的规则将“有效禁止”该汽车制造商在美国销售车辆，包括美国制造的汽车</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 23:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/biden-proposal-would-effectively-prohibit-sale-polestar-cars-us-automaker-says-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国敲定限制中国人工智能投资的规则并施加其他限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-finalizes-rules-curb-ai-investments-china-impose-other-restrictions-2024-10-28/</link><description>拜登政府周一表示，正在敲定规则，限制美国对中国人工智能和其他可能威胁美国国家安全的技术领域的投资。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 21:04:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-finalizes-rules-curb-ai-investments-china-impose-other-restrictions-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称，俄罗斯、中国和古巴的账户正在放大飓风错误信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/russian-chinese-cuban-accounts-are-amplifying-hurricane-misinformation-us-2024-10-28/</link><description>一名美国官员周一表示，在美国发生两场致命飓风后，与俄罗斯和中国有联系的影响者和古巴政府一直在放大错误信息，其中包括美国否认救灾索赔的虚假说法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 20:11:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/russian-chinese-cuban-accounts-are-amplifying-hurricane-misinformation-us-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥警告美国对中国汽车技术的禁令可能会损害汽车行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mexico-raises-concerns-about-us-plan-bar-chinese-vehicle-software-hardware-2024-10-28/</link><description>墨西哥政府周一对拜登政府出于国家安全考虑禁止在美国道路上使用关键中国软件和硬件的联网车辆的提议表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 17:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mexico-raises-concerns-about-us-plan-bar-chinese-vehicle-software-hardware-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员敦促审查中国来自光子技术的威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-urge-review-china-threat-photonics-technology-2024-10-28/</link><description>美国两党议员小组周一敦促商务部审查中国开发硅光子技术对国家安全的威胁，硅光子技术是一个快速发展的领域，可以加速人工智能的发展。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 13:12:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-urge-review-china-threat-photonics-technology-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国警方称，北京发生罕见持刀袭击事件，造成五人刺伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-stabbing-wounds-five-rare-knife-assault-chinese-police-say-2024-10-28/</link><description>据中央电视台报道，周一，中国首都北京发生一起持刀袭击事件，造成五人受伤，其中包括三名未成年人。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-stabbing-wounds-five-rare-knife-assault-chinese-police-say-2024-10-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>